<key>Eb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawi Jesuh thi a chuakmi cu, Keimah ca a sung bik, Tihnak le
 sualpalhnak chungin, Ka thlarau aa din cang.

[C1]
   Maw khuaruahhar tiva a luang, A kan Khamhbawi chungin, Van phak
   tiangin ka hla tha cu, &quot;Thi sung thletmi&quot; a si.

[V2]
 &quot;An sualnak le palhnak vialte, Ka ngaihthiam cang hna lai, Annih caah
 ka Fa a thi,&quot; tiah Pathian nih a ti.

[C2]
   Maw khuaruahhar tiva a luang, A kan Khamhbawi chungin, Van phak
   tiangin ka hla tha cu, &quot;Thi sung thletmi&quot; a si.

[V3]
 Philh khawh lomi ka sualnak nih, A ka tihter lai lo, A sung thi a
 chuakmi thawng in, Ngaihthiamnak ka hmuh cang.

[C3]
   Maw khuaruahhar tiva a luang, A kan Khamhbawi chungin, Van phak
   tiangin ka hla tha cu, &quot;Thi sung thletmi&quot; a si.

[V4]
 Zaang a dermi ka pumsa nih, Zawtnak kha tong hmanhseh, Khi thi chungah
 kaa dinh ahcun, Lungdai in ka thi lai.

[C4]
   Maw khuaruahhar tiva a luang, A kan Khamhbawi chungin, Van phak
   tiangin ka hla tha cu, &quot;Thi sung thletmi&quot; a si.</lyrics>
<title>THI SUNG CH136</title>
</song>